1.2
log
@lua_open() has been deprecated (but still available) in lua 5.1; but it's been
removed in lua 5.2. so prevent libquvi from breaking with newer lua's.
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
# $OpenBSD: Makefile,v 1.1.1.1 2011/11/11 15:21:24 jasper Exp $
